comment: interface to receive hotlist events on; use this on {@link #setHotlist}

methods.name: public void onFound(ScanResult[] results)
methods.comment:
indicates that access points were found by on going scans
         * @param results list of scan results, one for each access point visible currently

methods.name: public void onLost(ScanResult[] results)
methods.comment:
indicates that access points were missed by on going scans
         * @param results list of scan results, for each access point that is not visible anymore
